text: Kreshchenskoye () is a rural locality (a village) in Staroarzamatovsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 29 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 10 km from Mishkino, 6 km from Malonakaryakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Kreshchenskoye
